metadata.name: Classic Croc #1
metadata.description:
The Classic Crocs have not only a timeless look, they are also super limited. Only 100 of them will ever exist, all 1 of 1's. The Classic Croc is the first Cloudy Croc in this long-lasting collection. All Cloudy Crocs are originally illustrated by the artist, Keizzr.

Hold a Classic Croc for a 25% discount on the next type of Cloudy Croc.
